Assignment 2.3. Week 2: lists, tables and forms.

Take the website of the assignment 2.2 as foundation.
Add a comments section to one of your pages on which users can leave comments.
    e.g. https://dribbble.com/shots/5907097-Comment-Section

Add a table to an article, make sure it is relevant.
Add a contact form on the contact page on which the user can fill in their:
    - name
    - email
    - message

Make the website responsive.
Follow the checklist.
